      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Default Layouts\n- **Chain → Serpentine** (wrap every N nodes)\n- **Tree → Top-down layered**\n- **DAG → Left-right layered**\n\nPick one style per shape to keep consistency."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "layout-defaults",
