      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Key Parameters\n- **Direction:** top-down vs left-right\n- **Spacing:** node + layer spacing\n- **Wrap length:** chain nodes per column\n- **Edge routing:** orthogonal or straight"
      }
    },
